How to check if a port is listening?

Method 1 : check port status from server machine
>> netstat -tupnl

Method 2 : check port status fro client machine
>> nc -v -n 10.250.8.100 2222

Method 3 : perform TCP chat 
>> nc -l -p 5000             <--- run in server
>> nc 10.250.8.100 2222      <--- run in client



